title: Jim Hall Untold - Lessons Learned from Legendary Jazz Guitarist Jim Hall
description:
Take your jazz chops to the next level: book a call with Marc
https://nextlevel.jazzguitarlessons.net/ Jim Hall Untold - Lessons Learned from Jim Hall

Here's another video in the new "Untold" series on jazz guitar legends. The aim of this series is to provide the watcher with *more* that the basic biographical details about the player. In fact, "Untold" will give you practical musical and non-musical lessons to apply in your own life.

Basically, in the present episode ("Jim Hall Untold") we're asking the question "What can we learn from Jim Hall?"

Jim Hall was, perhaps, to most aesthetically refined jazz guitarist of the 20th. Check him out! 

Here's the Jim Hall page on the website:
JazzGuitarLessons.net/jim-hall.html

Top-5 Jim Hall Albums:
http://www.jazzguitarlessons.net/jim-halls-top-5-jazz-guitar-albums/

From more free lessons go to:
http://www.jazzguitarlessons.net

Full Jazz Guitar Mastery program:
https://learn.jazzguitarlessons.net/

Subscribe to JazzGuitarLessons.net Channel Here:
